        <strong class="font-medium">inviting,</strong> in contrast to large
        corporations. Furthermore, tontu is helping you
        <strong class="font-medium">save energy,</strong> so the colour
        <strong class="font-medium">green</strong> was used a lot to emphasise
        <strong class="font-medium">renewables and positivity.</strong>
